    CustomerInfo

    DebugExceptionMapper  
    EditAccountResource
    EditAccountResource class implements the REST service for EditAccountService The base path for this class is /editaccount

    The EvaluationInfo class implements the xml representation of an Evaluation, needed from EvaluationResource Every EvaluationInfo has: id routeId rating comment
    EvaluationResource
    EvaluationResource class implements the REST service for EvaluationService The base path for this class is /evaluation

    The LoginInfo class implements the xml representation of a login (for customer or taxi driver), needed from LoginResource Every LoginInfo has: username, password, lat, lon

    LoginResource class implements the REST service for LoginService The base path for this class is /login
    RegistrationResource
    RegistrationResource class implements the REST service for RegistrationService The base path for this class is /register

    RequestHandlingResource
    RequestHandlingResource class implements the REST service for RequestHandlingService The base path for this class is /request
